snippet.title: Gully (2019): Official Trailer, Crime, Drama
snippet.description:
Gully (2019)

R | 1h 21min | Crime, Drama | 4 June 2021 (USA)


Three teenagers from Los Angeles, all of whom had difficult childhoods, unleashed a hedonistic riot across the city over the course of 48 hours, unconstrained by social conventions. They take us on a wild voyage across Los Angeles, full of drugs and murder.


 Director: Nabil Elderkin
Writer: Marcus J. Guillory
Stars: Amber Heard, Charlie Plummer, Kelvin Harrison Jr.

snippet.title: Old - Official Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
Old
In Theaters July 23
https://www.old.movie

This summer, visionary filmmaker M. Night Shyamalan unveils a chilling, mysterious new thriller about a family on a tropical holiday who discover that the secluded beach where they are relaxing for a few hours is somehow causing them to age rapidly … reducing their entire lives into a single day.

The film stars an impressive international cast including Golden Globe winner Gael García Bernal (Amazon’s Mozart in the Jungle), Vicky Krieps (Phantom Thread), Rufus Sewell (Amazon’s The Man in the High Castle), Ken Leung (Star Wars: Episode VII—The Force Awakens), Nikki Amuka-Bird (Jupiter Ascending), Abbey Lee (HBO’s Lovecraft Country), Aaron Pierre (Syfy’s Krypton), Alex Wolff (Hereditary), Embeth Davidtz (The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo), Eliza Scanlen (Little Women), Emun Elliott (Star Wars: Episode VII—The Force Awakens), Kathleen Chalfant (Showtime’s The Affair) and Thomasin McKenzie (Jojo Rabbit).

Old is a Blinding Edge Pictures production, directed and produced by M. Night Shyamalan, from his screenplay based on the graphic novel Sandcastle by Pierre Oscar Lévy and Frederik Peeters. The film is also produced by Ashwin Rajan (Glass, AppleTV+’s Servant) and Marc Bienstock (Glass, Split). The film’s executive producer is Steven Schneider.

snippet.title: Storytelling@TheLibrary: "Amber Heard: An Actress and Human Rights Activist”
snippet.description:
Recorded on 22 October 2018 at the United Nations Library at Geneva, by the UN Library at Geneva, by UNTV & the UN Library Geneva.
Amber Heard is a world-renowned actress and an outspoken advocate against discrimination. A Human Rights Champion for the UN Human Rights Office, she lends her voice and support to promote the principles of the Universal Declaration of Human Rights (UDHR), which remains as powerfully relevant today as when it was adopted in 1948. Amber devotes her time off-screen to organizations such as Amnesty International and Art of Elysium, and most recently returned from a humanitarian trip to Jordan to visit Syrian refugees.

Welcome Remarks: Sigrun Habermann, UN Library Geneva. Introductory Remarks: Laurent Sauveur (Chief, External Outreach Service, UN Human Rights Office). Moderated by: Thomas Neufing (Chief, UNOG Centre for Learning and Multilingualism (CLM), United Nations Office at Geneva).

snippet.title: Aquaman and the last kingdom trailer|Amber Heard|Jason momoa
snippet.description:
Aquaman Movie Teaser Trailer! 

#Aquaman2 #JasonMomoa #DC 


►Note | All Footage Rights Reserved by 
© DC Comics

▶ Copyright Disclaimer: This video was made purely for fun. No copyright infringement intended. All copyright belongs to their respective owners. 

In 2018, James Wan’s Aquaman became a remarkably surprising smash hit. Nobody really knew what to expect from it for multiple reasons, given that it was following the disappointing release of Justice League; centered on a character who had never had his own live-action solo movie. Naturally, the excitement that the project generated immediately led Warner Bros. to solidify a future for the franchise, and within a few weeks of Aquaman’s release we learned about their plans to develop an Aquaman 2.

It’s typical for Hollywood studios to try and produce sequels as quickly as they possibly can. After all, they don’t want to let the heat of a burgeoning franchise die down, and the more time that passes means there’s more opportunities for audiences to be distracted by other big properties. That being said, Aquaman 2 is taking an extra minute to find its way to theaters, as Warner Bros. has announced that the blockbuster follow-up is currently scheduled to be released on December 22, 2022.

So, why is Aquaman 2 coming out about four years after its predecessor? For starters, producer Peter Safran has noted that the filmmakers behind the movie don’t feel the need to rush the project, believing that giving the sequel the most development time possible will ultimately be beneficial for the final product. But that’s not the only reason. Not only is the film going to need some legitimate time to actually get made from a logistics standpoint (it’s not super easy creating those underwater environments), but there are also many other DC Extended Universe titles in the works that the studio is developing between now and December 2022.

snippet.title: Amber Heard Joins SAMS Women's Mission to Lebanon, February 2019
snippet.description:
Last month, SAMS Goodwill Ambassador #AmberHeard joined our women’s health mission to #Lebanon, meeting with Syrian refugee women and underserved local communities who have limited access to the treatment they need. Amber has long advocated for women’s empowerment and ensuring the voices of those in need are amplified across the world.

During her visit, Amber visited informal settlements for Syrian refugees living in the Beka’a Valley and a local hospital in Tripoli where SAMS Volunteers treated 812 patients, performed 77 surgeries in addition to providing 166 cervical cancer screenings for women struggling to access these lifesaving services, free of charge.

Learn more about Amber's trip to Lebanon in the video below!

snippet.title: GULLY - Official Trailer 2021
snippet.description:
GULLY - Official Trailer 2021

Three teens living in LA, all victims of extreme childhoods, wreak a hedonistic riot across the city over the course of 48 hours, unbound by societal norms. They take us on a rip-roaring ride of drugs and murder across Los Angeles.
 
Director: Nabil Elderkin

About Yeh Un Dinon Ki Baat Hai:
-------------------------------------------------
Yeh Un Dinon Ki Baat Hai chronicles the adolescent romance between Naina and Sameer. The show explores the magic of 'first love'. Naina a quintessential good girl meets flamboyant Sameer in her school in Ahmedabad. She starts liking him the moment she meets him. But, when she watches Sameer hit another boy she has to tell the truth to the principal of the school. This results in Sameer's suspension and his dislike towards Naina. The same is followed by a series of misunderstanding between Sameer and Naina. In order to avenge his insults Sameer takes a bet with his friends that he will make Naina fall in love with him. What starts as a bet ends up in true love for Sameer as Naina cares for him like no one has ever done. When Naina gets to know about the bet she is heartbroken. Thus, begins Sameer's journey of transformation and penance. This show will be a closer exploration of everyday moments that these two share.

Project History & More Info: 

A friction fire made by the "Fire Plow" method is not as easy as it looks.  Practicing with the right woods and techniques is invaluable to being prepared for an actual emergency.  I used dried wild hibiscus wood, which in my experience is the easiest wood to do this with.  I've heard that dried sotol wood is also very easy.

The Samoans say that any type of wood can be used to make a friction fire, and it's important that both sticks come from the same piece of wood.  

I've tried many different woods and been successful with amazing amounts of smoke, but thus far haven't had any success in developing a coal.  It's probably my technique, which I hope I can master over time, but I've found very little information on the subject, and nobody who's actually done it with wood other than hibiscus or sotol.
#tkor #thekingofrandom

More about Gummibär
Gummibär, a funny and lovable cartoon character, is a green animated gummy bear with a multitude of talents. Whether he is singing, break dancing, or playing his tuba, both children and adults can't get enough of his funny gummy antics. His multi-lingual abilities have led to a huge International following and allow him to sing in 20 different languages including English, Hungarian, French, German, Spanish, Swedish, Portuguese, Czech, Slovak, Russian, and Hebrew with more to follow.

With close to 1 billion plays and counting, the video for "I Am A Gummy Bear" (The Gummy Bear Song) by Gummibär, has captured the hearts and minds of Internet users world-wide. Viewers of videos on YouTube, MySpace, and other social networking websites have made this animated short one of the most watched, most discussed, and most favorited videos on the Internet.

Initially a regional success in Hungary, it wasn't long before the catchy little 30 second animated clip found it's way onto social networking sites. In a matter of months, dozens, then hundreds, and now thousands of postings of the original video have popped up all over MySpace, YouTube, Facebook, and just about every online community that you can think of. In addition, thousands of people have created and posted user generated fan videos of themselves singing and dancing to The Gummy Bear Song as well.

snippet.title: Gully (Movie Review)
snippet.description:
Three years ago, music video director Nabil Elderkin, helmer behind videos for artists like Kanye West, Frank Ocean, Nicki Minaj and Arctic Monkeys, filmed his debut feature, a movie called Gully that is finally out on VOD. The film stars Kelvin Harrison Jr, Jacob Latimore, Charlie Plummer, Jonathan Majors, Amber Heard and Terrence Howard. It is a lot of things, but unfortunately, "really good" isn't one of them,

That said, it features an impressive cast, some strong ideas, interesting visuals and a lot of promise that everyone involved has greater work laying ahead in their respective futures. 

So...

Let's get into it...

Music courtesy of Epidemic Sound
"Full Moon Party Dot Mov" - Faison

Late Fees is dead. Long live Late Fees!
Triple Beam Streams, episode 3 is out, where we talk about 90 Day Fiancé, Love & Hip Hop Atlanta and SPIRAL! http://smarturl.it/rncradiowatch

I also guested on Spot Callers on RNC Radio to review Ultima Lucha TRES https://www.patreon.com/posts/spot-callers-may-51661368

I just started writing at Looper! Here's some recent movies I've reviewed for them:
Undine: https://www.looper.com/428407/undine-review-mermaids-need-love-too/
In The Heights: https://www.looper.com/433736/in-the-heights-review-a-musical-for-a-vaccinated-summer/

Keep up on my current watches: https://letterboxd.com/capnmagik/films/diary/

SUBSCRIBE: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7llcWZBhR9nvIzquktSzqg?sub_confirmation=1

Recent videos you may have missed!
Infinite (Movie Review): https://youtu.be/ftzdA6fpFZI
What We Talk About When We Talk About Bo Burnham's INSIDE: https://youtu.be/zpbhKZGUx2Q
Loki: Marvel's Best Show Yet?: https://youtu.be/zjb1j_d1mYI
The Conjuring: The Devil Made Me Do It (Movie Review): https://youtu.be/LWXiGcS9SpA

snippet.localized.title: Gully (Movie Review)
snippet.localized.description:
Three years ago, music video director Nabil Elderkin, helmer behind videos for artists like Kanye West, Frank Ocean, Nicki Minaj and Arctic Monkeys, filmed his debut feature, a movie called Gully that is finally out on VOD. The film stars Kelvin Harrison Jr, Jacob Latimore, Charlie Plummer, Jonathan Majors, Amber Heard and Terrence Howard. It is a lot of things, but unfortunately, "really good" isn't one of them,

That said, it features an impressive cast, some strong ideas, interesting visuals and a lot of promise that everyone involved has greater work laying ahead in their respective futures. 

So...

Let's get into it...

snippet.title: GULLY Official Trailer Reaction and discussion
snippet.description:
Amber Heard AND Terrence Howard?? Two arrested and admitted domestic abusers in the same film. Clearly, this director didn't give a f**k about people he cast being despicable human beings in real life.  What a shame for the rest of the cast.- Jaco

Powerful and unflinchingly honest, Gully is the explosive and timely story of three boyhood friends—Calvin, Nicky and Jesse—surviving an upbringing in LA’s roughest neighborhoods. Steeped in violence but united by friendship, together they find their escape in one out-of-control night of partying. But when the rampage stops, retribution begins. Starring Kelvin Harrison, Jr., Charlie Plummer, Jacob Latimore, Jonathan Majors, Amber Heard and Academy Award®-nominated Terrence Howard (Hustle & Flow).

Featuring: Amber Heard, John Corbett, Terrence Howard, Kelvin Harrison Jr., Charlie Plummer, Jonathan Majors, Travis Scott

snippet.title: GULLY Movie Review **SPOILER ALERT**
snippet.description:
Gay homosexuals Nick and Joseph spoil Gully - a 2019 American drama film, directed by Nabil Elderkin in his directorial debut, from a screenplay by Marcus J. Guillory.

Premise: Three teens living in LA, all victims of extreme childhoods, wreak a hedonistic riot across the city over the course of 48 hours, unbound by societal norms. They take us on a rip-roaring ride of drugs and murder across Los Angeles.

Find their podcast at the following:
    Anchor: https://anchor.fm/fish-jelly
    Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/show/388hcJA50qkMsrTfu04peH
    Apple Podcasts: https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/fish-jelly/id1564138767

Find them on Instagram:
     Nick (@ragingbells)
    Joseph (@joroyolo)
    Fish Jelly (@fishjellyfilms)

Nick is also the Lead Film Critic at Ioncinema (https://www.ioncinema.com/author/nicholas-bell) and a Tomatometer-approved critic on Rotten Tomatoes (https://www.rottentomatoes.com/critic/nicholas-bell/movies).

Cast:
Jacob Latimore as Calvin
Charlie Plummer as Nicky
Jonathan Majors as Greg
Kelvin Harrison Jr. as Jesse
Amber Heard as Joyce
Terrence Howard as Mr. Christmas
Zoe Renee as Keisha
Chastity Dotson as Angela
Chris Gann as Barett
Kashton Moore as Terry
John Corbett as Mr. Charlie

Cinematography by Adriano Goldman

snippet.title: БОЙКОТ УОРНЕР БРАЗЕРС, АКВАМЕН 2, ФАНТАСТИЧЕСКИЕ ТВАРИ 3 // ФАЙЛЫ ДЖОННИ ДЕППА
snippet.description:
ПЕТИЦИЯ ОБ ОТСТРАНЕНИИЕ ЭМБЕР ОТ РОЛИ В АКВАМЕН 2 https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2 #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
Поклонники Джонни Деппа объявили бойкот Голливуду, а точнее кинокомпании Уорнер Бразерс. Причины для этого всего две и они до банальности просты.
Первая причина заключается в том, что Уорнеры безосновательно уволили свою главную звезду «Фантастических тварей» из франшизы, не имея при этом  каких-либо веских доказательств его виновности.
Второй же причиной является то, что кинобоссы приняли отвратительное по своей сути решение оставить Эмбер Херд в Аквамене 2. Такое решение выглядит ещё более омерзительным после того, как скандальная актриса неоднократно признавалась на аудио записях в том, что она является абьюзером, иными словами домашним насильником и обидчиком. Улавливаете иронию? В судебном процессе представлены неоспоримые  доказательства того, что экс-жена Джонни Деппа всячески издевалась над ним в период  их совместного проживания, оскорбляла его физически и эмоционально, а так же нанесла увечье своему бывшему мужу. Но по иронии судьбы, карьеры лишился именно тот человек, которого обижали, над кем надругались, т.е. жертва, обидчик же сумел остаться в выигрыше: сохранить работу, настаивать на повышении гонораров, требовать для себя особого внимания, выходы на красные дорожки и всеобщего признания. Но это всё мисс абьюзер может требовать от киностудий, но не от зрителей.
ПЕТИЦИЯ ОБ ОТМЕНЕ ДОКУМЕНТАЛЬНОГО ФИЛЬМА О ПАДЕНИИ ДЖОННИ ДЕППА https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2/u/29138587
ПЕТИЦИЯ О ВОЗВРАЩЕНИИ ДЖОННИ К РОЛИ ДЖЕКА ВОРОБЬЯ https://www.change.org/p/walt-disney-we-want-johnny-depp-back-as-captain-jack-sparrow

ОБ ЭТОМ КАНАЛЕ:
Всегда нравились "Пираты Карибского моря"? Мечтал получше узнать Джонни Деппа и все, что с ним связано? Тогда советую подписаться на канал, посвященный американскому актеру Джонни Деппу!
Здесь ты узнаешь самые последние новости из жизни и творчества Джонни, а также факты о съемках фильмов, музыки, фотосессий и биографии. "Пираты Карибского моря", "Фантастические твари", "Город лжи", "В ожидании варваров"," Минамата" и о многих других работах Джонни Деппа тебе расскажет Владимир на канале "Файлы Джонни Деппа"! Переходи по ссылке и непременно подписывайся на этот потрясающий канал, да, и про уведомления не забудь, ведь это очень важно. Ссылка на канал здесь: https://youtube.com/c/JOHNNYDEPPFILES

snippet.title: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic - 'Ail-icorn' 🌡️ Official Short
snippet.description:
👀Watch more Pony Life episodes: https://bit.ly/MorePonyLife
❤️ Subscribe to the My Little Pony Channel: http://bit.ly/SubtoMLP
 
Welcome to the official home of My Little Pony & Equestria Girls! 🦄 Discover the magic ✨ of friendship with Twilight Sparkle, Rainbow Dash, Pinkie Pie, Rarity, Fluttershy, Applejack and friends. Join My Little Pony and subscribe today! Enjoy great MLP episodes here on My Little Pony Official channel where you can find: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic, My Little Pony Equestria Girls, MLP Stop Motion Shorts, Hello Pinkie Pie and our brand new Pony Life episodes!
 
🌈 Meet My Little Pony Rainbow Squads 🌈
 
Whether an alicorn like Twilight Sparkle, a unicorn like Rarity, a pegasus like Rainbow Dash and Fluttershy or an earth pony like Pinkie Pie and Applejack, get to know your favorite friends from My Little Pony and Equestria Girls!
 
My Little Pony - The Ponies:
💜 Twilight Sparkle: The leader of the Mane 6, she shares the magic of friendship with everypony she meets.
❤️ Fluttershy: A kind and gentle pony with a love of all creatures, big and small.
🧡 Applejack: Honest, friendly and sweet to the core!
💛 Pinkie Pie: The silliest pony around, she knows how to turn any frown upside down!
💚 Rarity: The resident fashionista, known for her beauty and generosity.
💙 Rainbow Dash: A loyal and dependable friend who is always ready for adventure!
 
My Little Pony - The Equestria Girls:
💜 Twilight Sparkle: Clever and curious, this Equestria Girl is always ready for a new challenge!
❤️ Fluttershy: Though shy and soft-spoken, this kind-hearted Equestria Girl will stand up for her friends no matter what!
🧡 Applejack: Sincere and self-confident, she is an Equestria Girl who stays true to herself!
💛 Rainbow Dash: The ultimate team player, this Equestria Girl enjoys having fun with her friends!
💚 Rarity: Trendy and fashionable, this Equestria Girl is all about generosity and fabulousity!
💙 Pinkie Pie: Entertaining and energetic, this Equestria Girl always makes sure her friends are having a great time!
 
 Twilight Sparkle's spring allergy manifests as a cold in her horn - every time she sneezes, something magical (and odd!) happens. After her uncontrollable horn-spray causes Rainbow Dash to speak in sound effects and nearly freezes Fluttershy, Pinkie arrives with a cure from Zecora - with a tiiiiny side effect.

For more My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic: https://goo.gl/YDKzr3

✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨

✨About Pony Life ✨

Explore the funny side of friendship with My Little Pony: Pony Life! 

Just like going to a friend’s house after school, the ponies spend most of their time at Sugarcube Corner. Here, Pinkie Pie serves up frosted cupcakes to the best customers in the world -- her friends! Together, the Mane 6 run into all sorts of cupcake conundrums, frosting fails, and magical mishaps. Welcome to the official home of My Little Pony & Equestria Girls! 🦄 Discover the magic ✨ of friendship with Twilight Sparkle, Rainbow Dash, Pinkie Pie, Rarity, Fluttershy, Applejack and friends. 🌈 Meet My Little Pony Rainbow Squads 🌈
 
Whether an alicorn like Twilight Sparkle, a unicorn like Rarity, a pegasus like Rainbow Dash and Fluttershy or an earth pony like Pinkie Pie and Applejack, get to know your favorite friends from My Little Pony and Equestria Girls!
 
My Little Pony - The Ponies:
💜 Twilight Sparkle: The leader of the Mane 6, she shares the magic of friendship with everypony she meets.
❤️ Fluttershy: A kind and gentle pony with a love of all creatures, big and small.
🧡 Applejack: Honest, friendly and sweet to the core!
💛 Pinkie Pie: The silliest pony around, she knows how to turn any frown upside down!
💚 Rarity: The resident fashionista, known for her beauty and generosity.
💙 Rainbow Dash: A loyal and dependable friend who is always ready for adventure!
 
My Little Pony - The Equestria Girls:
💜 Twilight Sparkle: Clever and curious, this Equestria Girl is always ready for a new challenge!
❤️ Fluttershy: Though shy and soft-spoken, this kind-hearted Equestria Girl will stand up for her friends no matter what!
🧡 Applejack: Sincere and self-confident, she is an Equestria Girl who stays true to herself!
💛 Rainbow Dash: The ultimate team player, this Equestria Girl enjoys having fun with her friends!
💚 Rarity: Trendy and fashionable, this Equestria Girl is all about generosity and fabulousity!
💙 Pinkie Pie: Entertaining and energetic, this Equestria Girl always makes sure her friends are having a great time!
 
 Twilight Sparkle's spring allergy manifests as a cold in her horn - every time she sneezes, something magical (and odd!) happens. After her uncontrollable horn-spray causes Rainbow Dash to speak in sound effects and nearly freezes Fluttershy, Pinkie arrives with a cure from Zecora - with a tiiiiny side effect.

snippet.title: Inside Bill Cosby’s Estate on His 1st Day Free From Prison
snippet.description: Bill Cosby, 83, may be planning to go back on the road with a one-man show. Cosby’s spokesperson Andrew Wyatt told Inside Edition in an exclusive interview following Cosby’s release from prison. The conviction was overturned on Wednesday, outraging many of the 60 women who allege he violated them. #InsideEdition

snippet.title: Amber Heard caught kissing a woman
snippet.description:
The star of "Aquamen" Amber Heard never hid from the public his bisexuality, alternating relations with men and women. The 33-year-old actress decided to start the New Year with a passionate romance with a representative of her gender.

Paparazzi caught Heard for hot kisses with 38-year-old cinematographer Bianca Butti. The couple fell into the lens of photographers when they left a luxury hotel in one of the resort towns of Southern California. The girls gently hugged and did not take their eyes off each other, then they left together on a vintage Ford Mustang Amber. It is noteworthy that the actress has been wearing a medical boot on her left foot since the beginning of the year. The details of the incident, after which she had to put in a cast, Hurd did not disclose.

About the new beloved actress, it is known that she is from Los Angeles and works as a graphic designer. Last year, Bianche was re-diagnosed with breast cancer. The first time she found out about a terrible diagnosis four years ago, but after treatment the disease receded. Now she again has to fight with oncology, and Hurd - steadfastly support his chosen one.

Recall that after a scandalous divorce from Johnny Depp and a relationship with billionaire Ilon Mask, Amber Heard enjoyed loneliness for a long time and did not advertise her personal life, apart from a romantic date with the director of the film “It”, Andres Musketti.

snippet.title: Mother of Australian boy raises awareness of bullying in viral video
snippet.description:

In a video that has attracted an outpouring of support, 9-year-old son Quaden Bayles, who has dwarfism, cries that he wants to kill himself after being taunted by a classmate over his height.

Potente e decisamente onesto, La Via è la storia esplosiva e attuale di tre amici d'infanzia, Calvin, Nicky e Jesse, che sopravvivono a una crescita nei quartieri più difficili di Los Angeles. Immersi nella violenza ma uniti dall'amicizia, insieme trovano una via di fuga in una notte di festeggiamenti fuori controllo. Ma quando la furia termina, inizia la punizione. ASSISTA EM HD (720p) (1080p)

S I N O P S E • 

Lisa Sue é a típica adolescente popular.
Uma jovem loira de olhos claros invejada pelas garotas e desejada pelos rapazes.
Mas os que poucos sabem, é que ela é uma jovem pobre que vive em um lar desestruturado.
Para esconder sua verdadeira realidade, ela acaba praticando Bullying com outras garotas da sua escola.

Uma dessas tenta suicídio e acaba ficando em coma.

Jack Moore ao saber dos motivos da tentativa de suicídio da filha resolve se vingar.
Após humilhar a garota na escola, ele a sequestra com a intenção de quebrá-la.

Ele a quebra de todas as formas possíveis.
Reconhecendo seus erros ela procura redenção.
Ele não acredita em seu arrependimento.
Em meio a vingança os dois se apaixonam e vivem uma tórrida paixão.

Será que o algoz liberará sua presa?
Será que um coração quebrado consegue perdoar e amar quem o feriu?

snippet.title: "IT'S TERRIBLE!" Amber Heard’s New Movie GETTING CRUSHED By Critics | Celebrity Craze
snippet.description:
Amber Heard’s New Movie GETTING CRUSHED By Critics | Celebrity Craze

Amber Heard's new movie does not seem to be pleasing critics. On top of that, she seems to be struggling to land movie roles. Could this be part of her ongoing legal issues with Johnny Depp?

With the initial court date being pushed back, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been given some more time in order to gather more evidence for their individual cases. For quite some time, the two were firing evidence at each other in order to win in court. 

Ever since the recent release of the footage of the LAPD officers from the penthouse night of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, things have not been looking all too bright for Amber Heard. Her team has been working tirelessly in order to back up her side, however Johnny Depp seems to have made the attempt to strike back.

Now it turns out that Amber Heard may have not written the statement or OP ED in accusations against Johnny Depp. This could another case of defamation or fraud. Let's break it down in today's video.

snippet.title: The Forever Purge - Official Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
One night is not enough. #TheForeverPurge in theaters July 2. Watch the trailer now.

--
https://uni.pictures/FOREVERPURGEFB
https://uni.pictures/FOREVERPURGETW
https://uni.pictures/FOREVERPURGEIG
https://uni.pictures/FOREVERPURGESITE


This summer, all the rules are broken as a sect of lawless marauders decides that the annual Purge does not stop at daybreak and instead should never end in The Forever Purge.  
 
Vaulting from the record-shattering success of 2018’s The First Purge, Blumhouse’s infamous terror franchise hurtles into innovative new territory as members of an underground movement, no longer satisfied with one annual night of anarchy and murder, decide to overtake America through an unending campaign of mayhem and massacre. No one is safe.  
 
Adela (Ana de la Reguera, Cowboys & Aliens) and her husband Juan (Tenoch Huerta, Days of Grace) live in Texas, where Juan is working as a ranch hand for the wealthy Tucker family. Juan impresses the Tucker patriarch, Caleb (Will Patton, Halloween), but  that fuels the jealous anger of Caleb’s son, Dylan (Josh Lucas, Ford v Ferrari).  
 
On the morning after The Purge, a masked gang of killers attacks the Tucker family—including Dylan’s wife (Cassidy Freeman, HBO’s The Righteous Gemstones), and his sister (Leven Rambin, The Hunger Games), forcing both families to band together and fight back as the country spirals into chaos and the United States begins to disintegrate around them.  
 
From a screenplay by franchise creator and narrative mastermind James DeMonaco, The Forever Purge is directed by Everardo Gout, writer-director of the award-winning thriller Days of Grace. The film is produced by the franchise’s founding producers: Jason Blum for his Blumhouse Productions; Platinum Dunes partners Michael Bay, Andrew Form and Brad Fuller; and Man in a Tree duo James DeMonaco and his longtime producing partner Sébastien K. Lemercier. The film’s executive producers are Marcei A. Brown, Everardo Gout and Jeanette Volturno. Universal Pictures presents, in association with Perfect World Pictures, a Platinum Dunes/Blumhouse/Man in a Tree production.

Amber Heard se meteu em uma polêmica e foi pega mentindo no flagra mais uma vez.

A atriz, que interpreta a Mera nos cinemas, postou uma foto falsa enganando os fãs sobre uma suposta preparação para o início das filmagens de Aquaman 2.

Assista o vídeo e entenda!

snippet.title: GULLY | Official Trailer | Paramount Movies
snippet.description:
Available on Digital and on Demand June 8 and in select theaters June 6

Powerful and unflinchingly honest, Gully is the explosive and timely story of three boyhood friends—Calvin, Nicky and Jesse—surviving an upbringing in LA’s roughest neighborhoods. Steeped in violence but united by friendship, together they find their escape in one out-of-control night of partying. But when the rampage stops, retribution begins. Starring Kelvin Harrison, Charlie Plummer, Jacob Latimore, Jonathan Majors, Amber Heard and Academy Award®-nominated Terrence Howard (Hustle & Flow).

Featuring: Amber Heard, John Corbett, Terrence Howard, Kelvin Harrison Jr., Charlie Plummer, Jonathan Majors, Travis Scott

© Paramount Movies

Magnificent
Magnificent

I was born
I was born to be with you
In this space and time
After that and ever after I haven't had a clue
Only to break rhyme
This foolishness can leave a heart black and blue

Only love, only love can leave such a mark
But only love, only love can heal such a scar

I was born
I was born to sing for you
I didn't have a choice but to lift you up
And sing whatever song you wanted me to
I give you back my voice
From the womb my first cry, it was a joyful noise ...

Only love, only love can leave such a mark
But only love, only love can heal such a scar

Justified till we die, you and I will magnify

snippet.description:
GOLUI (গলুই) - Official Trailer 2021 | Shakib Khan | Puja Cherry | SA Haque Alik - (Fan-Made)

Golui (Fan-Made) Trailer Made By

Cast
Shakib Khan
Puja Cherry
